{
  "stem": "8784.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There is a good chance that he was selected out to go on to another concentration camp because he was young and looked very strong.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There is a good chance that he was selected to, to remain alive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But when he noticed his family on the other side of the street, he made a dash to join them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And on crossing the street, he was shot down in the middle of the street.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So there was an eyewitness telling me the story that my older brother was, in fact, killed in the ghetto itself.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the rest of the family-- the fate of the rest of the family was totally unknown to me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I began life inside of a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this is 1943.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I'm 17 years old.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Never been away far from my family, never knowing how to get along on my own, I found myself in the, in a concentration camp where I practically didn't know anyone.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And even if I did, they were lost in that concentration camp because there were thousands upon thousands of people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I don't have a good idea of how many thousands of people there were at that particular time, but if I were to guess at it, there were well over 20,000 people in the ghetto, in the concentration camp at that time.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I became an inmate of this concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Life was unbearable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Constant fear.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Food in short supply.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "All alone.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Looking undernourished and not in the best of health, because the war was on for three years already.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I'm not really equipped to deal with the heavy burden of a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But there I was.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
